  <van-form>
     <van-field
    v-model="username"
    name="游戏名称"

    placeholder="此处最好填入您的真实姓名或者外号"
    :rules="[{ required: true, message: '请填写用户名' }]"
  />
  </van-form>
</template>

  data(){
    return {
      username: '',
    }
  }

}
</script>
